CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 11, 1957, pg. 14, reads: "25 Years of Song - One of the features of the program sponsored by Wesley Center Cathedral Choir was an honorarium, citing members who have served 25 years or more... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Man and woman holding small gift boxes, possibly members of Wesley Center AME Zion Church choir posed in church
